1. create a new folder (root) for this project

2. create a subfolder named "venv" (venv) to store the virtual environment

3. open vscode, create a new python file save it under root

4. check out terminal, cd to root and paste the following to initialize venv:

		python3 -m venv /path/to/new/virtual/environment

	files will be populated under folder venv.

5. activate venv by typing the following into terminal:

		source /path/to/new/virtual/environment/bin/activate

	(! tips: to print current working path, use command "pwd")

6. install bs4 through terminal:

	pip install beautifulsoup4

7. install requests lib:

	pip3 install requests

8. write python code in FileDownloader.py

9. run by typing the following on terminal under root folder:

	python3 FileDownloader.py